OL,3,CPolice concern over teenagers
OL,4,Cillegally buying knives online
OL,6,FUnderage teenagers buying knives
OL,7,Fonline remains "a really concerning
OL,8,Fpicture" for police, with illegal
OL,9,Fdealers selling weapons via social
OL,10,Fmedia.
OL,12,FThe national lead for policing knife
OL,13,Fcrime, Commander Stephen Clayman, said
OL,14,Fforces in England and Wales are keen
OL,15,Fto cut off the supply of weapons as
OL,16,Fpart of efforts to stop injuries and
OL,17,Fdeaths.
