OL,3,CPolice concern over teenagers
OL,4,Cillegally buying knives online
OL,6,FKnives are being sold illegally to
OL,7,Funder 18s via social media channels
OL,8,Fincluding TikTok, Snapchat and those
OL,9,Frun by Meta, he said.
OL,11,FSpeaking ahead of a week of police
OL,12,Faction to tackle knife crime, he told
OL,13,Fjournalists: "It's still a really
OL,14,Fconcerning picture in terms of the
OL,15,Faccessibility of knives online."
OL,17,FAll police forces in England and Wales
OL,18,Fwill ramp up action for a week this
OL,19,Fmonth as part of Operation Sceptre,
OL,20,Fand again in November.
