OL,6,FWriting in the Daily Telegraph,
OL,7,Fpolicing minister Chris Philp has
OL,8,Fcalled on police forces to make more
OL,9,Fuse of stop and search.
OL,11,F"The police must use the powers
OL,12,Favailable to them without fear or
OL,13,Ffavour," he wrote.
OL,15,FOfficial figures show that knife crime
OL,16,Frose by 7% in the year to December
OL,17,F2023.
