OL,4,Cillegally buying knives online
OL,6,FIn the year to March 2023, 82% of
OL,7,Fteenage homicide victims were killed
OL,8,Fwith a knife, compared to 73% in the
OL,9,Fprevious year.
OL,11,FThe Home Office announced on Tuesday
OL,12,Fthat it would give #3.5 million
OL,13,Fadditional funding for research and
OL,14,Fdevelopment of new technologies which
OL,15,Fwould allow knives to be detected from
OL,16,Fa distance when a suspect passes
OL,17,Fthrough two points.
