OL,6,FAn additional #547,863 will also be
OL,7,Fgiven to the Metropolitan Police to
OL,8,Ffund four more live facial recognition
OL,9,Fcamera vans.
OL,11,FLaws around zombie knives, machetes
OL,12,Fand swords are to be tightened up from
OL,13,FSeptember, giving police greater
OL,14,Fpowers to seize weapons found in
OL,15,Fprivate properties.
