OL,6,FIt will be illegal to possess, sell,
OL,7,Fmanufacture or transport zombie-style
OL,8,Fknives and machetes, and the maximum
OL,9,Fpenalty for the possession of these
OL,10,Fand other banned weapons will also
OL,11,Fincrease from six months to two years.
OL,13,FA surrender and compensation scheme is
